by SpacePossum at 2015-10-21T15:33:36Z

Looks good to me :+1:

If I understand/read you code correctly you won't insert any place holders for the spacing of double arrows for nested arrays if such an an array is on one line, correct?
So a small future improvement could be removing extra white space around an double arrow if found in an nested array (for example in something like this:

```php
<?php
$formMapper->add(1, 2, array(
    "keys" => array(
        array(5, 123, array(10   => array(12 => false))),
)));
```
)

