by keradus at 2015-10-21T18:51:47Z

Yeah, your solution was to detect nested array, I add a check if nested array is single-line.

The fixer does not remove extra spaces, so I would keep it that way. If one want to remove extra spaces around `=>` he has separated fixer for that ;)

Thanks for approval ! Fixer is quite tricky.
